Package: section508.gov
Title: Governmentwide Section 508 Assessment Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the GSA Governmentwide Section 508
    Assessment data. Provides access to FY2023 and FY2024 reporting entity
    response data including maturity and conformance scores.
